cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on neural machine translation. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves the use of neural networks to improve translation. Additionally, it may fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of attention mechanisms in neural networks. Finally, it could also be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it involves the use of weight sharing methods to improve translation.
